      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Hot Topic Hooligans",
        "Client": "Gossiping Lady",
        "Description": "I heard from my brother\u0027s mother\u0027s\r\ncousin that the Frost Islands are\r\ncrawling with monsters these days.\r\nAnd get this, my mailman\u0027s uncle\r\nwas just ruffed up out there the other\r\nday. It used to be such a nice place.\r\nWish someone\u0027d do something about it...",
        "Target": "Slay a total of 20 Zamite or Bnahabra",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Hooligans !",
        "Client": "Comm\u00E8re",
        "Description": "D\u0027apr\u00E8s le cousin de la m\u00E8re de mon\r\ndemi-fr\u00E8re, il para\u00EEt que l\u0027Archipel\r\nde glace grouille de monstres ces\r\nderniers temps. Et tiens-toi bien,\r\nle facteur de mon oncle y aurait\r\nm\u00EAme \u00E9t\u00E9 agress\u00E9 ! Ah, si seulement\r\n\u00E7a pouvait \u00EAtre calme comme avant...",
        "Target": "Tuer 20 Zamite ou Bnahabra",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Hai saputo l\u0027ultima?",
        "Client": "Dama pettegola",
        "Description": "Il cugino del fratello di mia\r\nmadre mi ha detto che le Isole\r\nghiacciate pullulano di\r\nmostri. E l\u0027altro giorno, il\r\npostino di mio zio \u00E8 stato\r\naggredito laggi\u00F9. Era un posto\r\nbellissimo! Puoi intervenire?",
        "Target": "Uccidi 20 Zamite o Bnahabra in totale",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Kleine Monster, gro\u00DFe Sache",
        "Client": "Tratschende Dame",
        "Description": "Ich hab vom Cousin der Mutter meines\r\nBruders geh\u00F6rt, dass es auf den Frost-\r\ninseln vor Monstern nur so wimmelt.\r\nUnd halt dich fest: Der Onkel meines\r\nPostboten ist da neulich verkloppt\r\nworden. Es war mal so ein netter Ort.\r\nWenn doch nur jemand was t\u00E4te...",
        "Target": "Erlege insgesamt 20 Zamiten\r\noder Bnahabra.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "V\u00E1ndalos candentes",
        "Client": "Maruja local",
        "Description": "El primo de la madre de mi\r\nhermano me ha dicho que hay\r\nmuchos monstruos en las Islas\r\nheladas. Y el t\u00EDo de mi cartero\r\nest\u00E1 mosquead\u00EDsimo. Con lo\r\ntranquilo que era antes ese\r\nlugar... Hay que hacer algo.",
        "Target": "Abate un total de 20 Zamite o Bnahabra",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
